  "id": "s2_s1_forest_fire_progression",
  "summary": "Multitemporal Sentinel-2/Sentinel-1 forest fire progression mapping using openEO.",
  "description": "Fuses Sentinel-2 optical indices at t1 with the Sentinel-1 VH backscatter change between t1 and t2 to map forest fire progression under cloud cover, classifying each pixel as newly burned, vegetated background, already-burned bare, or recovering. Converted from the Sentinel Hub S2/S1 Forest Fire Progression evalscript by Max Kampen."
